metadata.name: Little Feelings NFT #1
metadata.description: Little Feelings, an NFT project from the heart. 10,000 curious Sprouts descended from the skies eager for your affection. Nurture them and give them a new home. Feed your Sprout, grow with them, and reward yourself with an everlasting friendship. Sprouts, a fabled community of magical creatures, each born without feelings that souls in the mortal world can only understand. Sprouts have been rumored to come from a mountain so high that reaches into the clouds where a sacred tree rests at the peak. The unusual appetite of Sprouts creates an endless hunger to consume anything before them and the only thing left in their sights was their home. They started at the branches and ended at the roots. And, before they even knew, the 10,000 Sprouts were descending from the sky without fear or direction. Striking the dirt, one by one, the Sprouts found themselves wandering about the unchartered land where unexpectedly they bumped into YOU. Adopt your Sprout and embrace what Little Feelings are really about.
